title: The Grand (made 2007) (released 2008) (poker movie)
description:
An improvisational comedy (directed by Zak Penn) with an ensemble cast playing characters competing in an actual poker tournament. The focus of the film is a poker tournament at the Golden Nugget in Las Vegas in which real poker matches were played by the actors. The film's script did not specify the winner of the tournament, and the film's ending was determined by the game played on set.

This is a hard-to-find film, and is a single unpacked AVI file.

English soft subtitles (SRT) included.
